Invocation Name: wacky wisdom
des:
Welcome to the world of Wacky Wisdom. With this skill, you can listen to random bits of wacky wisdom straight from your Alexa device.

Simply open the skill by saying: 
“Alexa, open Wacky Wisdom” or
"Alexa, Launch Wacky Wisdom" or
"Alexa, Start Wacky Wisdom" and make your selection from there,

Thanks, and we hope you enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
